  "page": "Togarion Bar Emmon",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bar_Emmon\" title=\"House Bar Emmon\"><img alt=\"House Bar Emmon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Bar_Emmon.svg/50px-House_Bar_Emmon.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Bar_Emmon.svg/75px-House_Bar_Emmon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/House_Bar_Emmon.svg/100px-House_Bar_Emmon.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Togarion Bar Emmon<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Terrible</span></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bar_Emmon\" title=\"House Bar Emmon\"><img alt=\"House Bar Emmon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Bar_Emmon.svg/50px-House_Bar_Emmon.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/ad/House_Bar_Emmon.svg/75px-House_Bar_Emmon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/ad/House_Bar_Emmon.svg/100px-House_Bar_Emmon.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nTogarion Bar Emmon</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nKing</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nTogarion the Terrible</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Bar_Emmon\" title=\"House Bar Emmon\">House Bar Emmon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nDaughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Josua_Massey\" title=\"Josua Massey\">Josua Massey</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Togarion Bar Emmon</b>, known as <b>Togarion the Terrible</b>, was an <a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a> warlord of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bar_Emmon\" title=\"House Bar Emmon\">House Bar Emmon</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Togarion_Bar_Emmon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Andal_invasion\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal invasion\">Andal invasion</a>, Togarion the Terrible established a small kingdom of his own north of the <a href=\"/index.php/Blackwater_Bay\" title=\"Blackwater Bay\">Blackwater Bay</a>. However, he soon found himself hard-pressed by the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Darklyn\" title=\"House Darklyn\">Darklyn</a> king of <a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale\" title=\"Duskendale\">Duskendale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Across the bay, <a href=\"/index.php/Qarlton_III_Durrandon\" title=\"Qarlton III Durrandon\">Qarlton III Durrandon</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Storm_King\" title=\"Storm King\">Storm King</a>, reconquered <a href=\"/index.php/Massey%27s_Hook\" title=\"Massey&#39;s Hook\">Massey's Hook</a> following four generations of war, having slain the Hook's last king <a href=\"/index.php/Josua_Massey\" title=\"Josua Massey\">Josua Massey</a>. Sensing weakness to the south, Togarion wed Josua Softspear's daughter and crossed Blackwater Bay with all his power to establish a new kingdom on the Hook. He built his own castle of <a href=\"/index.php/Sharp_Point\" title=\"Sharp Point\">Sharp Point</a> at the Hook's end, whilst driving the stormlanders from <a href=\"/index.php/Stonedance\" title=\"Stonedance\">Stonedance</a> and installing his wife's brother as a puppet <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lord</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>While Torgarion the Terrible was the first Andal warlord to invade the <a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Kingdom of the Storm</a>, others soon followed that brought graver concerns to Qarlton III than the reloss of Massey's Hook.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> In time, the Storm Kings would reconquer Togarion's small kingdom, and Sharp Point and Stonedance became vassals of <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Togarion_Bar_Emmon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_stormlands:_andals_in_the_stormlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Stormlands: Andals in the Stormlands.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabaegon.27s_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Aegon's Conquest.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>New title</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> King of <a href=\"/index.php/Sharp_Point\" title=\"Sharp Point\">Sharp Point</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Duram_Bar_Emmon\" title=\"Duram Bar Emmon\">Duram Bar Emmon</a> </b><br /><small><i><b>as <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Sharp_Point\" title=\"Lord of Sharp Point\">Lord of Sharp Point</a> </b></i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403151504\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.082 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.279 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1170/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 13506/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9689/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1821/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensi